                    "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-traits=\"poison\" data-pf2-label=\"Scalathrax Venom DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span>;</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds;</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} (1 round);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> clumsy 1 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1} (1 round);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> clumsy 1 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 2} (1 round)</p>\n</div>"
